   The lesson? If you find your credit report sullied by someone
else's data, do what Thomas did, said attorney Mike Baxter,
co-counsel in Thomas' case: Doc, document, document.

   Steven Kipnis of DBL Realtors, Sunset, represented the buyers;
Carl Williams of the same firm had the listing and represented
McDonnell in buying.

